OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,FA bomb disposal expert says three
OL,7,Funexploded bombs discovered next to a
OL,8,FGuernsey housing development could be
OL,9,Fextremely dangerous to the residents.
OL,11,FThe bombs were discovered on Route
OL,12,FIsabelle, with documented evidence
OL,13,Fthat they were dropped on 3 March 1941.
OL,15,FIn 2019, the States of Guernsey sent a
OL,16,Fspecialist team to examine the field
OL,17,Fwhen the nearby Wellington Close
OL,18,Fhousing development was being built.
