OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,FHowever, bomb disposal expert and
OL,7,Fformer soldier Ben Remfrey claims that
OL,8,Fthis was just a shallow non-intrusive
OL,9,Fsearch of 3 metres which was not
OL,10,Fthorough enough.
OL,12,FHe explains: "(The bombs) are still
OL,13,Fthere because no one has taken the
OL,14,Ftime and the effort to locate and then
OL,15,Fdispose of them.
OL,17,F"The Home Affairs department decided
OL,18,Fthey would do a tick-the-box, shallow,
OL,19,Fnon-intrusive survey.
