OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,F"They thought that the bombs being in
OL,7,Fthe deep ground meant that they would
OL,8,Fnot be a threat, and that is
OL,9,Fcompletely ignorant."
OL,11,FThe States responded that specialists
OL,12,Fdid not rule out the bombs' existence
OL,13,Fand that a second, more in-depth
OL,14,Fsurvey was considered.
OL,16,FThey have also told ITV News that a
OL,17,Fnew specialist has been invited to
OL,18,Fmeet with them next week to discuss
OL,19,Fthe issue.
