OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,FSandra Silvestre says she and her
OL,7,Fneighbours are nervous, and that if
OL,8,Fshe had known about the devices, she
OL,9,Fwouldn't have bought her house.
OL,11,FShe adds: "It's a complete shock to
OL,12,Fhear that, 83 years after they were
OL,13,Fdropped.
OL,15,F"I would have liked to have had more
OL,16,Ffrom the developer, which I haven't
OL,17,Fspoken to yet but I might have to,
OL,18,Fdepending on what goes forward."
