OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,FBen has also suggested that the longer
OL,7,Fthe bombs are left in the field, the
OL,8,Fmore likely the devices could
OL,9,Fdeteriorate and pose further risk.
OL,11,FHe says: "Between the three bombs,
OL,12,Fthere is about 1000 pounds of TNT and
OL,13,Fthe likelihood is that there would be
OL,14,Fa detonation of the other bombs which
OL,15,Fwould be catastrophic to the residents.
OL,17,F"Permission was given knowing it was
OL,18,Fthere. It is negligence. They are
OL,19,Frisking people's lives."
OL,21,FStates of Guernsey response:
