OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey said they
OL,7,Fbecame aware of the unexploded bombs
OL,8,Fin 2018.
OL,10,FThey state: "In June 2019, the States
OL,11,Fof Guernsey commissioned a private,
OL,12,Fspecialist company to conduct a non-
OL,13,Finvasive survey of the land the bombs
OL,14,Fwere alleged to have landed in. That
OL,15,Fsurvey was also extended to the
OL,16,Fsurrounding fields.
OL,18,F"This survey found no evidence of any
OL,19,Fordnance, nor did it find any evidence
OL,20,Fof a detonated device referred to in
OL,21,Fthe historic letters.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
