OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1728505160
OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,F"The specialists acknowledged that
OL,7,Fthis survey did not rule out the
OL,8,Fexistence of the ordnance, however,
OL,9,Fthe recommendation was made that a
OL,10,Fsecond survey could be carried out.
OL,12,F"If a second survey involving
OL,13,Fexcavation was to have been carried
OL,14,Fout, a cordon stretching to Waitrose
OL,15,Fon the Rohais and to the hospital
OL,16,Fwould have to be put in place, which
OL,17,Fwould have caused disproportionate
OL,18,Fdisruption to the community.
