OL,3,CExpert says inaction over unexploded
OL,4,Cbombs is 'risking people's lives'
OL,6,F"The States of Guernsey and Guernsey
OL,7,FPolice take the risk of historic
OL,8,Fordnance very seriously, as evidenced
OL,9,Fby the regular action of the Police's
OL,10,FEOD team.
OL,12,F"In this case, however, there is no
OL,13,Fstrong evidence that these devices
OL,14,Fexist and the States of Guernsey has
OL,15,Falready conducted precautionary work
OL,16,Fto ensure the risk to the community is
OL,17,Fminimal."
